    "body": "### Description\n\ntailwindcss lsp doesn't work well with tailwindcss v4 (removal of tailwind config file). I read this [issue](https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-intellisense/issues/1377) from their intellisense and tried to fix it in neovim with\n```lua\nvim.lsp.config('tailwindcss', {\n  settings = {\n    tailwindCSS = {\n      classFunctions = { \"cva\", \"cx\" },\n      classRegex = {\n        { \"Class\\\\(([^)]*)\\\\)\", '[\"`]([^\"`]*)[\"`]' },\n        { \"ClassX\\\\(([^)]*)\\\\)\", '[\"`]([^\"`]*)[\"`]' },\n        { \"ClassIf\\\\(([^)]*)\\\\)\", '[\"`]([^\"`]*)[\"`]' },\n        { \"Classes\\\\(([^)]*)\\\\)\", '[\"`]([^\"`]*)[\"`]' },\n      },\n      configFile = vim.fs.find(\n        { \"globals.css\" },\n        { path = vim.fs.joinpath(LazyVim.root.get(), \"packages/ui/src/styles\") }\n      ),\n    },\n  }}\n)\n```\nbut the lsp.log gave me this message:\n```txt\n Invalid `experimental.configFile` configuration, not initializing\n```",
